<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Appeach" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Appeach,</orth> to impeach, inform against: <cit><quote>I will a. the villain,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 5.2.79" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 2, 79</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.2.79" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 2, 79</bibl> Absolutely: <cit><quote>your passions have to the full --ed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 1.3.197" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 3, 197</bibl></cit>, i. e. informed against you.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>